title: Formula 1 2015 The F1 Show August 14th 360p HEVC-[f1d] mkv
description:
The F1 Show mid-season review for 2015 continues in this Aug. 14th episode.

Note: The source file used for encoding has audible compression artifacts, i.e., being too lossy. I have encoded the audio at a higher bit-rate to try to compensate, but it's a bit of a silk purse/sow's ear thing. I can't make it better than the source, which doesn't sound all that great (maybe a 6/10). Sorry, but it's the only source I've found out there.
